Player Configuration Files
==========================

An overview of the various configuration files for running Player on the
real robots. Configuration files for each driver is located in the
appropriate driver/ subdirectory.

scorpion.cfg
------------
This configuration file loads all the drivers implemented for the
Scorpion robot.

hdaps-scorpion.cfg
------------------
Loads the HDAPS driver in addition to the drivers loaded by scorpion.cfg

cave.cfg
--------
Matches the Stage Configuration File and example with same name.
